  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 10th level, you can choose the other option you didn't choose with your <em><strong>Lethal Precision</strong></em> feature. This grants you access to the other option with <em><strong>Self Sufficient Armory</strong></em>.</p><p>Additionally, you can attack with your <em><strong>Symbiotic Weapons</strong></em> as a bonus action when you would take the attack action or use them as a component in a Taijutsu or Bukijutsu. You can also change the damage type of these weapons to be Necrotic or that of a nature release you possess (Water=Cold).</p><p>Finally, your Passenger gains a number of seal slots equal to your proficiency bonus, which can only affect your <em><strong>Symbiotic Weapons.</strong></em></p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
